%% Indexer -> wallet-service integration: reliable balance reconciliation
%% Author: Yashvardhan Gaur
%% Two-phase persist, confirmation gating, outbox -> Redis Stream, reorg-safe consumer
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant RPC as Chain RPC
  participant IDX as Indexer (BTC/ETH/TRON)
  participant DB as Postgres (indexer)
  participant OB as event_outbox
  participant RS as Redis Stream<br/>indexer:balance-updates
  participant WC as wallet-service<br/>BalanceUpdateConsumer
  participant WDB as Postgres (wallet)

  Note over IDX,DB: Phase 1 — PREPARE (no DB writes)
  IDX->>RPC: fetch blocks (parallel, bounded)
  RPC-->>IDX: blocks + logs
  IDX->>IDX: parse, compute balance deltas, build events

  Note over IDX,OB: Phase 2 — PERSIST (one atomic txn / AtomicBatchSize=10 blocks)
  IDX->>DB: BEGIN
  IDX->>DB: write blocks, tx_refs, balances
  IDX->>OB: insert events (deterministic event_id, status=pending/dispatchable)
  IDX->>DB: COMMIT (all-or-nothing)

  Note over OB,RS: Drain (immediate + retry loop, exp backoff 2s..300s)
  OB->>OB: claim rows FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED
  OB->>RS: XADD data=<balance_update json> (MAXLEN ~100k)
  RS-->>OB: ok -> status=success / else reschedule

  Note over WC,WDB: Consume (group=wallet-service)
  WC->>RS: XREADGROUP > (batch, block 5s)
  RS-->>WC: balance_update event
  WC->>WC: chainSymbolMap normalise (eth/evm/sepolia->eth ...)
  WC->>WDB: UpsertWithHeight — accept only if block_height > stored
  WC->>RS: XACK
  WC-->>WC: publish webhook:balance-updated (async)

  Note over RPC,WDB: Reorg path
  IDX->>RPC: parent-hash mismatch detected
  IDX->>DB: walk back to common ancestor, delete orphaned range (atomic)
  IDX->>OB: emit subtype=reorg_rollback (corrected balance at ancestor height)
  OB->>RS: XADD
  WC->>WDB: ForceUpsert — bypass guard, reset height DOWN to ancestor
  Note over WC,WDB: canonical chain replays forward via normal guard

  Note over WC: Recovery — pendingRecoveryLoop every 30s.<br/>XAUTOCLAIM messages idle over 5m.<br/>Transient errors stay in PEL and retry.<br/>"not tracked" -> ACK and skip
